robot
---------------------------------------

Robot is in the early stages of life. üçï


Talking to the robot
---------------------------------------

Posting to <myserver.com>/action with a request body of:

{
  actions: {
    comment: {
      issue: <number>,
      repo: <owner/repo-name>,
      body: <your-message>
    }
  }
}


Working on the robot
---------------------------------------

* npm i
* npm run dev
